<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your BookSwap Password</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset styles */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      background-color: #f5f7fa;
    }

    /* Container styles */
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    /* Header styles */
    .email-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 150px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Content styles */
    .email-content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #555555;
    }

    /* Button styles */
    .reset-button {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      background-color: #eed47e;
      color: #2c3e50;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .reset-button:hover {
      background-color: #e6c55c;
    }

    /* Security notice styles */
    .security-notice {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666666;
    }

    /* Footer styles */
    .email-footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888888;
    }

    .social-links {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .social-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 10px;
      color: #666666;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Responsive styles */
    @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .email-container {
        padding: 10px;
      }

      .email-content {
        padding: 20px 15px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .reset-button {
        padding: 12px 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-container">


    <div class="email-content">
      <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>

      <p>Hello,</p>

      <p>We received a request to reset your password for your BookSwap account. To proceed with resetting your
        password, click the button below:</p>

      <a href="<%= link %>" class="reset-button">Reset Password</a>

      <p>This password reset link will expire in 1 hour for security reasons. If you didn't request this password reset,
        please ignore this email or contact our support team if you have concerns.</p>

      <div class="security-notice">
        <strong>Security Tip:</strong>
        <p>For your security, please ensure that:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>You never share your password with anyone</li>
          <li>Use a unique password that you don't use for other websites</li>
          <li>Include numbers, letters, and special characters in your new password</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>This is an automated email, please do not reply.</p>

      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="#" class="social-link">Facebook</a>
        <a href="#" class="social-link">Twitter</a>
        <a href="#" class="social-link">Instagram</a>
      </div>

      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> BookSwap. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>University of Stuttgart, Germany</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>